// SKIP: Shields are not modeled as an `ArmorCategory` in the spec (`ArmorCategory` only covers `LightArmor | MediumArmor | HeavyArmor`), and there is no Shield Master feat type or shield-proficiency flag. The connection between `lacksArmorProficiency` and Dex-save disadvantage is also not integrated into `pSaveModifiers`, making the core Q&A rule (lack of shield proficiency → Dex save disadvantage) unrepresentable with existing spec functions.